1.title: The First Pencilmation
1.plot: This is the very first episode of Pencilmation in which the pencil draws the original Pencilmate and takes him on a wild adventure.

2.title: The Pen Is Mightier
2.plot: In Pencilmation #2 "The pen is mightier" Pencilmate comes back for a new adventure. This time he rebels against the pencil and wins...but can he win against a pen and a marker?

3.title: MC Hammered
3.plot: A cranky doodle monster which gets all the reasons to be even more mad... From being pursued by a walking hammer and running nails to being unfairly treated by a mysterious machine, it is not his day.

4.title: Amour Than Enough
4.plot: A funny love triangle between an ordinary doodle, a beautiful doodlette and a rock star. It all takes place in a very "lively" house, but who will win who?

5.title: To Beard or Not to Beard
5.plot: To beard or not to beard? That is the question.... When two identical doodles fight to get the most facial hairs... Does a beard really make a guy stronger?

6.title: Turtles in Time
6.plot: Hank Hanky's first ever appearance. In this episode the pencil confronts him to the inevitable notion of Time hence making Hank a character that only likes to live in the present!

7.title: Malice in Wonderland
7.plot: Drawing inspiration from the famous story where cake can make you grow, rabbits like tea and hats are full of surprises, you never know what's behind the door...

8.title: DiscOh-No!
8.plot: Pencilmation #8 "DiscOh-No!" tells you what to do when a cranky doodle comes and crash the party.

9.title: Love at First Write
9.plot: In Pencilmation #9 "Love at first write" the pencil helps two lovelorn doodles connect giving them access to many new ways of communication. Too many maybe?

10.title: Hook, Line, and Stinker
10.plot: Pencilmation #10 "Hook, Line and Stinker" after spending all his afternoon fishing for nothing, a man is finally rewarded for his perseverance... A mermaid will make his dreams come true...
